Changed paths:
 M http://src.chromium.org/viewvc/native_client/trunk/src/native_client/src/untrusted/pnacl_irt_shim/nacl.scons?r1=7846&amp;r2=7845&amp;pathrev=7846

Make the pnacl_irt_shim build Windows friendly.

1) Use os.path.join() instead of assuming separator '/'
2) Resolve the glob '*.idl' using env.Glob instead of relying on shell expansion (which does not occur on Windows).

